Generate highly comprehensive lesson plan details for Session #1 out of 5 total sessions, each running for 45 minutes.
Subject: Physics
Grade/Level: Class XI / Class XII / 12th Grade / Science
Active Chapters/Topics being taught: ["Chapter–5: Magnetism and Matter","Chapter–6: Electromagnetic Induction","Chapter–7: Alternating Current","Chapter–8: Electromagnetic Waves","Chapter–9: Ray Optics and Optical Instruments","Chapter–10: Wave Optics","Chapter–11: Dual Nature of Radiation and Matter","Chapter–12: Atoms","Chapter–13: Nuclei","Chapter–14: Semiconductor Electronics: Materials, Devices and Simple Circuits"]

Generation Preferences:
- Include Learning Outcomes: YES
- Include Introduction Hook: YES
- Include Theory & Explanations: YES
- Include Assessments with Keys: YES
- Include Homework Exercises: YES
- Include Materials Setup (PowerPoint slides, study guide nodes): YES

Be educational, engaging, structured, and pedagogical. Provide exact questions and answers (Assessment Key, Assignment Key). Use actual textbook topics.
Make sure each block of details is populated.


Return valid JSON only. Match this target schema shape exactly:
{
  "id": "unique-session-id",
  "sessionNumber": 1,
  "title": "Vibrant, educational title for this session",
  "duration": 45,
  "learningOutcomes": [
    "Specific action-oriented objectives"
